@CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5014

GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Products API

### GET All Products (Paginated)
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Product by ID
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### POST Create Product
POST {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supermarketId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "name": "Organic Milk 1L",
  "brand": "FreshFarm",
  "category": "Dairy",
  "barcode": "1234567890123",
  "isFreshFood": true
}

###

### POST Create Product with Images (MarketStaff flow)
### Form fields: SupermarketId, Name, Brand, Category, Barcode, IsFreshFood, files (multiple)
### Use Postman: Body -> form-data, add product fields + files
POST {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Products/with-images
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

###

### PUT Update Product
PUT {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supermarketId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "name": "Organic Milk 1L Updated",
  "brand": "FreshFarm",
  "category": "Dairy",
  "barcode": "1234567890123",
  "manufactureDate": "2025-01-15T00:00:00Z",
  "expiryDate": "2025-02-15T00:00:00Z",
  "originalPrice": 5.99,
  "suggestedPrice": 4.99,
  "status": 0
}

###

### DELETE Product
DELETE {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Supermarkets API

### GET All Supermarkets (Paginated)
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Supermarkets?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Supermarket by ID
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Supermarkets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### POST Create Supermarket
POST {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Supermarkets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "FreshMart Downtown",
  "address": "123 Main Street, City Center",
  "latitude": 10.762622,
  "longitude": 106.660172,
  "contactPhone": "+84901234567"
}

###

### PUT Update Supermarket
PUT {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Supermarkets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "FreshMart Downtown Updated",
  "address": "123 Main Street, City Center",
  "latitude": 10.762622,
  "longitude": 106.660172,
  "contactPhone": "+84901234567",
  "status": 0
}

###

### DELETE Supermarket
DELETE {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Supermarkets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### MarketStaff API

### GET All MarketStaff (Paginated)
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/MarketStaff?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### GET MarketStaff by ID
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/MarketStaff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### POST Create MarketStaff
POST {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/MarketStaff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "supermarketId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "position": "Store Manager"
}

###

### PUT Update MarketStaff
PUT {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/MarketStaff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "supermarketId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "position": "Senior Store Manager"
}

###

### DELETE MarketStaff
DELETE {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/MarketStaff/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Upload API (R2)

### POST Test upload to R2 (any file, returns Key and Url - no ProductImage)
### Form field: file (IFormFile)
POST {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Upload/test
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

###

### POST Upload image to R2 (product image - requires productId)
### Form fields: file (IFormFile), productId (Guid)
POST {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

###

### GET All files in R2 bucket
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Upload/files
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Images by Product ID
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Upload/product/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/images
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Pre-signed URL for image (by ProductImageId) - use returned URL in browser
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Upload/image/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/presign?expiryMinutes=60
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Pre-signed URL by key (from test upload response)
GET {{CloseExpAISolution.API_HostAddress}}/api/Upload/presign?key=products/xxx_filename.png&expiryMinutes=60
Accept: application/json

###
